 64.8526%; height: 24px;\"><span data-path-to-node=\"3,10,1,0\">Ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t cao c\u1ea5p<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.1474%; height: 24px;\"><strong>Th\u1eddi gian b\u00e0n giao<\/strong><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 64.8526%; height: 24px;\"><span data-path-to-node=\"3,11,1,0\">D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Qu\u00fd 4\/2027<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 10px;\">\n<td style=\"width: 35.1474%; height: 10px;\"><strong>Ph\u00e1p l\u00fd<\/strong><\/td>\n<td style=\"width: 64.8526%; height: 10px;\"><span data-path-to-node=\"3,12,1,0\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e2u d\u00e0i (ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam), 50 n\u0103m (ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i)<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n","tq_list":[{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2021\/07\/icon_2.png","title":"Ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0","desc":"C\u00f4ng ty TNHH \u0110\u1ea7u t\u01b0 D\u1ef1 \u00e1n Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ho\u00e0n"},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2021\/07\/icon_2.png","title":"Ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n d\u1ef1 \u00e1n","desc":"DXMD Vi\u1ec7t Nam"},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2021\/07\/icon_2.png","title":"Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng b\u1ea3o l\u00e3nh","desc":"Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng MB "}],"tq_over_bg":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/can-ho-fenica-di-an.jpg","tq_over_content":"<div style=\"width: 1920px;\" class=\"wp-video\"><video class=\"wp-video-shortcode\" id=\"video-5688-1\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loop autoplay preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"video\/mp4\" src=\"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/video-du-an-fenica.mp4?_=1\" \/><a href=\"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/video-du-an-fenica.mp4\">https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/video-du-an-fenica.mp4<\/a><\/video><\/div>\n","vt_title":"V\u1ecb tr\u00ed","vt_title_sub":"K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng","vt_img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/vi-tri-du-an-fenica.jpg","vt_content":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ecda l\u1ea1c tr\u00ean m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Tr\u1ea7n Quang Di\u1ec7u, <strong>c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Fenica<\/strong> n\u1eb1m \u1edf t\u1ecda \u0111\u1ed9 giao thoa kinh t\u1ebf tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u1eefa TP. D\u0129 An, TP. Thu\u1eadn An v\u00e0 TP. Th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c. T\u1eeb d\u1ef1 \u00e1n, c\u01b0 d\u00e2n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn giao th\u00f4ng huy\u1ebft m\u1ea1ch nh\u01b0 Qu\u1ed1c L\u1ed9 1K, Qu\u1ed1c L\u1ed9 13, DT743.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3>Ti\u1ec7n \u00edch ngo\u1ea1i khu<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>1km \u0111\u1ebfn: Ch\u1ee3 T\u00e2n Long, Ga Metro An Ph\u00fa (tuy\u1ebfn Metro s\u1ed1 1), Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec3u h\u1ecdc T\u00e2n \u0110\u00f4ng Hi\u1ec7p, UBND ph\u01b0\u1eddng T\u00e2n \u0110\u00f4ng Hi\u1ec7p<\/li>\n<li>1-3km \u0111\u1ebfn: Vincom Plaza D\u0129 An, KCN S\u00f3ng Th\u1ea7n 1 &amp; 2, B\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n Ho\u00e0n M\u1ef9 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng tr\u00ean tr\u1ee5c DT743.<\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3-5km \u0111\u1ebfn: L\u00e0ng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Qu\u1ed1c gia TP.HCM, Si\u00eau th\u1ecb GO! D\u0129 An, KCN VSIP 1, B\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n \u0110a khoa D\u0129 An, Ga S\u00f3ng Th\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Tuy\u1ebfn Metro s\u1ed1 1 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i: D\u1ef1 \u00e1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1ch ga An Ph\u00fa (thu\u1ed9c tuy\u1ebfn metro Su\u1ed1i Ti\u00ean &#8211; B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng) kho\u1ea3ng 850m, mang \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf di chuy\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i.<\/li>\n<li>Cao t\u1ed1c &amp; V\u00e0nh \u0111ai: Ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 5 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng M\u1ef9 Ph\u01b0\u1edbc &#8211; T\u00e2n V\u1ea1n (n\u1eb1m trong quy ho\u1ea1ch V\u00e0nh \u0111ai 3). Trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, d\u1ef1 \u00e1n s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i l\u1edbn t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn Cao t\u1ed1c TP.HCM &#8211; Th\u1ee7 D\u1ea7u M\u1ed9t &#8211; Ch\u01a1n Th\u00e0nh.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","mb_title":"M\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n Fenica","mb_title_sub":"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1","mb_content":"<p>X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng tr\u00ean qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea5t 5.537m\u00b2, d\u1ef1 \u00e1n Fenica D\u0129 An bao g\u1ed3m 2 th\u00e1p c\u0103n h\u1ed9 cao 22 t\u1ea7ng v\u00e0 2 t\u1ea7ng h\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ed7 xe r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i. M\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ch\u1ec9 48,5%, ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean cho m\u1ea3ng xanh, m\u1eb7t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng gian ti\u1ec7n \u00edch.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Fenica D\u0129 An l\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea5t 4 m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0 l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n cao t\u1ea7ng duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean tr\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Tr\u1ea7n Quang Di\u1ec7u hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebf v\u00e0 th\u00e1p c\u0103n h\u1ed9 ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng l\u00f9i khoa h\u1ecdc, gi\u00fap 100% c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn Panorama kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb che ch\u1eafn, \u0111\u00f3n tr\u1ecdn \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 lu\u1ed3ng gi\u00f3 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng cho kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_5693\" style=\"width: 1210px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5693\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-5693\" src=\"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-1-du-an-can-ho-fenica.jpg\" alt=\"M\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea7ng 1 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Fenica D\u0129 An\" width=\"1200\" height=\"825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-1-du-an-can-ho-fenica.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-1-du-an-can-ho-fenica-300x206.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-1-du-an-can-ho-fenica-1024x704.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-1-du-an-can-ho-fenica-768x528.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-5693\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea7ng 1<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_5694\" style=\"width: 1210px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5694\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-5694\" src=\"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-2-du-an-can-ho-fenica.jpg\" alt=\"M\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea7ng 2 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Fenica D\u0129 An\" width=\"1200\" height=\"825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-2-du-an-can-ho-fenica.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-2-du-an-can-ho-fenica-300x206.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-2-du-an-can-ho-fenica-1024x704.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-2-du-an-can-ho-fenica-768x528.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-5694\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea7ng 2<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_5695\" style=\"width: 1210px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5695\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-5695\" src=\"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-3-21-du-an-can-ho-fenica.jpg\" alt=\"M\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea7ng 3-21 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Fenica D\u0129 An\" width=\"1200\" height=\"825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-3-21-du-an-can-ho-fenica.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-3-21-du-an-can-ho-fenica-300x206.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-3-21-du-an-can-ho-fenica-1024x704.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-3-21-du-an-can-ho-fenica-768x528.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-5695\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea7ng 3-21<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_5696\" style=\"width: 1210px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5696\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-5696\" src=\"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-22-du-an-can-ho-fenica.jpg\" alt=\"M\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea7ng 22 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Fenica D\u0129 An\" width=\"1200\" height=\"825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-22-du-an-can-ho-fenica.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-22-du-an-can-ho-fenica-300x206.jpg 300w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-22-du-an-can-ho-fenica-1024x704.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/mat-bang-tang-22-du-an-can-ho-fenica-768x528.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-5696\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea7ng 22<\/p><\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","mb_img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/phoi-canh-du-an-fenica-di-an.jpg","mb_bg":false,"ti_title":"Ti\u1ec7n \u00edch c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Fencica","ti_title_sub":"Chu\u1ea9n s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i","ti_desc":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m trung &#8211; cao c\u1ea5p d\u00e0nh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1ebb, Fenica t\u00edch h\u1ee3p chu\u1ed7i ti\u1ec7n \u00edch &#8220;All-in-one&#8221; ngay t\u1ea1i 2 t\u1ea7ng kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebf v\u00e0 khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean d\u1ef1 \u00e1n:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i 2 t\u1ea7ng, si\u00eau th\u1ecb ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c d\u00e3y shophouse s\u1ea7m u\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ed3 b\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u1ef1c, khu c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u1ea3nh quan, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ea1o b\u1ed9 c\u00e2y xanh.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khu v\u1ef1c BBQ ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi, l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp m\u1eb7t gia \u0111\u00ecnh cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u00f2ng Gym &amp; Yoga trang b\u1ecb hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, khu vui ch\u01a1i tr\u1ebb em (Kidzone), nh\u00e0 tr\u1ebb n\u1ed9i khu.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u1eafm b\u1eaft xu h\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i khi t\u00edch h\u1ee3p Lounge &#8211; Co-working (kh\u00f4ng gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chung) v\u00e0 Livestream room.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","ti_list":[{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/cong-vien-fenica.jpg","title":"C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean n\u1ed9i khu","sub_title":"","content":""},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/bbq-tai-fenica-di-an.jpg","title":"Khu BBQ","sub_title":"","content":""},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/ho-boi-can-ho-fenica-di-an.jpg","title":"H\u1ed3 b\u01a1i","sub_title":"","content":""},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/khu-vui-choi-tre-em-tai-du-an-fenica-di-an.jpg","title":"khu vui ch\u01a1i tr\u1ebb em","sub_title":"","content":""},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/phong-livestream-tai-fenica-di-an.jpg","title":"Ph\u00f2ng livestream","sub_title":"","content":""},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/phong-sinh-hoat-cong-dong-fenica.jpg","title":"Ph\u00f2ng sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng","sub_title":"","content":""},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/phong-tap-gym-tai-can-ho-fenica-di-an.jpg","title":"Ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp Gym","sub_title":"","content":""},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/sanh-don-khach-tai-can-ho-fenica-di-an.jpg","title":"S\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3n kh\u00e1ch","sub_title":"","content":""},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/trung-tam-thuong-mai-tai-fenica.jpg","title":"Trung t\u00e2m th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i","sub_title":"","content":""}],"sp_title":"C\u0103n h\u1ed9 Fenica","sp_title_sub":"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf - Gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n - Thanh to\u00e1n","sp_desc":"<h3>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u0103n h\u1ed9 Fenica D\u0129 An<\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u1ef1 \u00e1n Fenica cung c\u1ea5p 579 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u1edbi di\u1ec7n t\u00edch linh ho\u1ea1t, h\u01a1n 85% l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch v\u1eeba v\u00e0 nh\u1ecf, c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u \u1edf th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cho thu\u00ea:<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111a d\u1ea1ng:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>1PN: Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ~43.09m\u00b2.<\/li>\n<li>1PN+1: Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ~48.82 &#8211; 50.48m\u00b2 (t\u00edch h\u1ee3p th\u00eam kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111a n\u0103ng l\u00e0m ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ho\u1eb7c kho).<\/li>\n<li>2PN: Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ~66.06 &#8211; 66.31m\u00b2.<\/li>\n<li>3PN: Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch ~99.01m\u00b2.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed vu\u00f4n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">g v\u1ee9c, l\u00f4 gia v\u00e0 ban c\u00f4ng t\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3>Ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n b\u00e0n giao cao c\u1ea5p<\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>H\u1ec7 c\u1eeda &amp; Kh\u00f3a:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> C\u1eeda ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1eeda g\u1ed7 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00e1y (th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u An C\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng); trang b\u1ecb kh\u00f3a c\u1eeda th\u00f4ng minh cao c\u1ea5p t\u1eeb Yale\/Kaadas (\u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng: v\u00e2n tay, m\u1eadt m\u00e3, th\u1ebb t\u1eeb, kh\u00f3a c\u01a1).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>S\u00e0n nh\u00e0:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 khu v\u1ef1c b\u1ebfp l\u00e1t g\u1ea1ch 80x80cm (th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Amy Gres cao c\u1ea5p); to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 l\u00e1t s\u00e0n g\u1ed7 d\u00e0y 12mm (An C\u01b0\u1eddng).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb v\u1ec7 sinh:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> B\u00e0n giao \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Innoci (\u0110\u1ee9c) bao g\u1ed3m lavabo, b\u00e0n c\u1ea7u, v\u00f2i r\u1eeda, sen t\u1eafm&#8230;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng li\u00ean l\u1ea1c n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 (Intercom):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t s\u1eb5n, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an ninh t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho t\u1eebng c\u0103n h\u1ed9.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","events":false,"sp_list":[{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/can-ho-1pn-fenica.jpg","title":"C\u0103n h\u1ed9 1 PN"},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/can-ho-1pn-plus-fenica.jpg","title":"C\u0103n h\u1ed9 1 PN+"},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/can-ho-1pn-plus-goc-fenica.jpg","title":"C\u0103n h\u1ed9 1 PN+ g\u00f3c"},{"img":"https:\/\/dxmdvietnam.vn\/files\/2026\/04\/ca